lyrics:
(Verse 1) 
Enigmatic grin, eyes alight with desire She moves like a panther, untamed by fire A touch that captivates, a smile that holds you fast Uninhibited, she'll forever hold you, forever cast

(Chorus) 
Under her spell, you'll lose all control Intoxicated by her, she'll steal your soul Enigmatic woman, a dangerous game In her embrace, you'll forever remain
